Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(主演:菅野真穗)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,（子宫觉醒）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很久不见\N要很久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,上次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.28,0:00:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是比我想像的更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,男优很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,男优很厉害？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,男优的什么地方厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是满足了，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想要怎么样做爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为上次比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是第一次吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果激烈一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更舒服对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天多多指教\N多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这胸也太开了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以叫男优进来了吧？\N拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真有礼貌\N没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想要激烈一点啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢？\N还想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想要被摸\N摸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不说不做哦\N用力一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以咬吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸开始急促了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不够对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不够\N这样对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,直柔软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下爱好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,用力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还要用力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已经很用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要用力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都是汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃，这里最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,被舔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,会更舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,直有弹性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,放松点，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自己看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这小穴肯定喜欢粗暴一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么自慰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,用手指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,打开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,张开，对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,张开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢激烈的话，自己说岀来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢激烈一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了，高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,继续舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这里湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
